1
00:00:00,398 --> 00:00:02,698
(To welcome the new year of 2026)

2
00:00:03,698 --> 00:00:06,208
(the crew prepared an ambitious trip.)

3
00:00:06,908 --> 00:00:08,868
(A spinning wheel?)

4
00:00:09,708 --> 00:00:12,238
(Such ghastly keywords)

5
00:00:13,148 --> 00:00:15,748
(They're given a chance to manipulate it.)

6
00:00:16,178 --> 00:00:18,818
(New Year Plan Manipulation Squad)

7
00:00:19,418 --> 00:00:22,248
(They compete in missions to win slots...)

8
00:00:22,718 --> 00:00:26,087
(and sabotage the crew's plan.)

9
00:00:26,088 --> 00:00:27,327
Why won't you play properly?

10
00:00:27,328 --> 00:00:28,827
(However, the members struggle...)

11
00:00:28,828 --> 00:00:30,957
(with the extreme difficulty.)

12
00:00:30,958 --> 00:00:32,258
Of course it's squid!

13
00:00:32,698 --> 00:00:36,098
(Eventually, they resort to wiretapping.)

14
00:00:36,998 --> 00:00:39,268
(Distrust deepens)

15
00:00:39,368 --> 00:00:40,438
Ottawa.

16
00:00:40,568 --> 00:00:43,008
(Seon Ho does unexpectedly well.)

17
00:00:43,908 --> 00:00:45,207
- Okay.
- Okay!

18
00:00:45,208 --> 00:00:47,548
(The members gain momentum...)

19
00:00:48,078 --> 00:00:50,748
(and obtain 5 slots on the spinning wheel.)

20
00:00:51,518 --> 00:00:53,847
(Can they manipulate...)

21
00:00:53,848 --> 00:00:56,188
(the new year plan?)

22
00:00:57,518 --> 00:01:00,688
(2 Days 1 Night)

23
00:01:00,958 --> 00:01:02,758
- Let's get moving.
- Okay.

24
00:01:02,928 --> 00:01:04,057
Let's climb inside.

25
00:01:04,058 --> 00:01:06,997
(Se Yoon folds himself into the car.)

26
00:01:06,998 --> 00:01:07,998
My gosh.

27
00:01:08,368 --> 00:01:09,737
Move one of your shoulders.

28
00:01:09,738 --> 00:01:11,297
- Jong Min...
- Come on!

29
00:01:11,298 --> 00:01:13,468
(Save us)

30
00:01:14,068 --> 00:01:15,568
- Gosh.
- How is it back there?

31
00:01:16,008 --> 00:01:17,338
Check.

32
00:01:17,978 --> 00:01:19,237
I can't shut the door.

33
00:01:19,238 --> 00:01:20,678
- Move to the side.
- Leave it open.

34
00:01:20,848 --> 00:01:22,177
- The door...
- "Leave it open."

35
00:01:22,178 --> 00:01:23,947
Don't lean sideways. Someone must lean forward.

36
00:01:23,948 --> 00:01:25,177
- Okay, I'm done.
- Hang on.

37
00:01:25,178 --> 00:01:26,748
- We're fine.
- Okay.

38
00:01:26,988 --> 00:01:28,447
What will you do now?

39
00:01:28,448 --> 00:01:29,718
Wear your seat belt.

40
00:01:30,288 --> 00:01:31,417
Let's drive fast.

41
00:01:31,418 --> 00:01:32,718
Fast. Drive!

42
00:01:33,528 --> 00:01:37,328
(After much struggling, they set off.)

43
00:01:38,158 --> 00:01:39,928
I can't even speak over here.

44
00:01:40,068 --> 00:01:41,368
I can't breathe.

45
00:01:41,928 --> 00:01:43,337
Shall I sit selfishly...

46
00:01:43,338 --> 00:01:44,537
- and see what happens?
- Wait.

47
00:01:44,538 --> 00:01:46,018
- Shall I be inconsiderate?
- Try it.

48
00:01:46,168 --> 00:01:47,438
- Shall I?
- Yes.

49
00:01:48,168 --> 00:01:50,538
(If he just lowers his arm...)

50
00:01:50,908 --> 00:01:51,908
(Yelling)

51
00:01:53,308 --> 00:01:55,948
This is madness. The door might pop open.

52
00:01:56,218 --> 00:01:57,347
(Laughing)

53
00:01:57,348 --> 00:01:59,148
"The door might pop open."

54
00:02:00,318 --> 00:02:04,358
It's suffocating. So suffocating!

55
00:02:04,788 --> 00:02:06,787
It's a nice sight, though.

56
00:02:06,788 --> 00:02:08,288
- Like a family.
- What?

57
00:02:09,758 --> 00:02:12,358
Is this almost the last game if we think about the wheel?

58
00:02:13,028 --> 00:02:14,028
- Right?
- Right.

59
00:02:14,029 --> 00:02:15,767
It's our last chance to win slots.

60
00:02:15,768 --> 00:02:17,298
Yes. We must win lots here.

61
00:02:17,798 --> 00:02:21,038
The moment we win more slots for the wheel,

62
00:02:21,838 --> 00:02:23,138
let's write insanely good stuff.

63
00:02:23,708 --> 00:02:25,107
Yes, and let's reduce the bad ones.

64
00:02:25,108 --> 00:02:26,477
Whether they accept it or not.

65
00:02:26,478 --> 00:02:28,307
We might end up with no sleep.

66
00:02:28,308 --> 00:02:29,577
They must accept it too.

67
00:02:29,578 --> 00:02:31,318
The stuff the crew wrote.

68
00:02:33,048 --> 00:02:35,187
- They're unjust.
- Right.

69
00:02:35,188 --> 00:02:37,387
- We can be equally unjust.
- Correct.

70
00:02:37,388 --> 00:02:39,158
- From our point of view.
- That's right.

71
00:02:39,488 --> 00:02:40,527
This is our last shot.

72
00:02:40,528 --> 00:02:41,887
We're heading to the base camp.

73
00:02:41,888 --> 00:02:43,628
(Solemn, serious)

74
00:02:44,798 --> 00:02:48,928
(The resolute manipulation squad arrives at...)

75
00:02:49,128 --> 00:02:50,597
Is this our rendezvous point?

76
00:02:50,598 --> 00:02:51,798
Is this it?

77
00:02:52,698 --> 00:02:55,967
This is Chuncheon's Mount Gubong Cafe Street...

78
00:02:55,968 --> 00:02:58,378
from where you can see the whole city.

79
00:02:58,578 --> 00:02:59,877
It's beautiful.

80
00:02:59,878 --> 00:03:02,508
(A refreshingly open view)

81
00:03:02,848 --> 00:03:04,317
It's a famous spot to take...

82
00:03:04,318 --> 00:03:05,717
- social media pics.
- It's nice.

83
00:03:05,718 --> 00:03:06,718
It's pretty.

84
00:03:06,719 --> 00:03:08,247
The manipulation squad...

85
00:03:08,248 --> 00:03:10,017
is about to face the final mission.

86
00:03:10,018 --> 00:03:12,387
- Yes, it's the last one.
- Good. Let's do it.

87
00:03:12,388 --> 00:03:13,727
So far,

88
00:03:13,728 --> 00:03:16,327
you managed to win five spinning wheel slots.

89
00:03:16,328 --> 00:03:18,157
- Yes.
- Just eight would be fine.

90
00:03:18,158 --> 00:03:20,267
If you clear the last mission,

91
00:03:20,268 --> 00:03:22,967
- we'll give you three more slots.
- Good.

92
00:03:22,968 --> 00:03:24,498
Yes. Eight is worth fighting for.

93
00:03:24,738 --> 00:03:27,708
The 2026 New Year Plan Manipulation Squad's final mission.

94
00:03:27,768 --> 00:03:29,977
- The Golden Bell Merge.
- What?

95
00:03:29,978 --> 00:03:31,837
I'll explain each task.

96
00:03:31,838 --> 00:03:34,047
- This is the basic setting.
- Okay.

97
00:03:34,048 --> 00:03:35,647
I'll explain each in turn.

98
00:03:35,648 --> 00:03:37,948
Participant one must do sit-ups.

99
00:03:38,318 --> 00:03:40,287
He must eat the hanging donut...

100
00:03:40,288 --> 00:03:42,118
while avoiding the spinning stick...

101
00:03:42,288 --> 00:03:43,758
before heading to the jump rope.

102
00:03:44,388 --> 00:03:45,717
- He must jump rope too?
- Yes.

103
00:03:45,718 --> 00:03:47,087
Participants 2 and 3...

104
00:03:47,088 --> 00:03:48,527
must move table tennis balls.

105
00:03:48,528 --> 00:03:49,897
You take the bull fight pose...

106
00:03:49,898 --> 00:03:51,527
and move the balls with your mouth.

107
00:03:51,528 --> 00:03:52,857
You must move three.

108
00:03:52,858 --> 00:03:54,497
Then participant two goes to the jump rope.

109
00:03:54,498 --> 00:03:56,437
Just one and not both?

110
00:03:56,438 --> 00:03:57,997
Participants 3 and 4...

111
00:03:57,998 --> 00:03:59,337
must do a trust exercise.

112
00:03:59,338 --> 00:04:00,967
You have to hit and drop...

113
00:04:00,968 --> 00:04:03,177
a mandarin from the top of one's head.

114
00:04:03,178 --> 00:04:06,138
You must do that within five spins.

115
00:04:06,408 --> 00:04:08,547
- Then...
- One goes to the rope.

116
00:04:08,548 --> 00:04:09,618
Yes.

117
00:04:09,718 --> 00:04:11,617
Participants 4 and 5...

118
00:04:11,618 --> 00:04:13,017
play human zero.

119
00:04:13,018 --> 00:04:15,047
Defend successfully twice in a row...

120
00:04:15,048 --> 00:04:16,817
- before joining the jump rope team.
- Twice in a row?

121
00:04:16,818 --> 00:04:19,487
If you all jump the rope five times in a row,

122
00:04:19,488 --> 00:04:20,928
you clear the final mission.

123
00:04:21,258 --> 00:04:23,557
- You get three shots.
- Okay.

124
00:04:23,558 --> 00:04:25,197
Who's good at human zero?

125
00:04:25,198 --> 00:04:26,467
- Jong Min?
- Jong Min.

126
00:04:26,468 --> 00:04:28,727
- Jong Min, you can do that.
- Okay.

127
00:04:28,728 --> 00:04:31,437
I'll be the glove that tries to catch him out.

128
00:04:31,438 --> 00:04:33,207
Who wants to be the first one?

129
00:04:33,208 --> 00:04:34,467
- I think...
- Seon Ho.

130
00:04:34,468 --> 00:04:36,537
Seon Ho said that was easy.

131
00:04:36,538 --> 00:04:37,538
It's perfect for him, then.

132
00:04:37,539 --> 00:04:39,977
- I think that's really easy too.
- Do you?

133
00:04:39,978 --> 00:04:41,007
You're not a bad option either.

134
00:04:41,008 --> 00:04:42,378
It's you or Seon Ho.

135
00:04:42,548 --> 00:04:43,577
(Joon tries first.)

136
00:04:43,578 --> 00:04:44,777
Of course this is doable.

137
00:04:44,778 --> 00:04:46,388
- This can be done.
- It can be done.

138
00:04:47,448 --> 00:04:48,818
It's hard.

139
00:04:52,488 --> 00:04:53,588
It's hard.

140
00:04:54,158 --> 00:04:56,758
Hey, this is hard. It's impossible.

141
00:04:56,958 --> 00:04:57,958
(Laughing)

142
00:04:58,158 --> 00:05:00,197
Hey, it looks like you got slapped.

143
00:05:00,198 --> 00:05:02,198
(Trying with all his might)

144
00:05:02,328 --> 00:05:03,438
It's impossible.

145
00:05:04,438 --> 00:05:06,238
I can't do it. Hey, Seon Ho.

146
00:05:06,298 --> 00:05:08,108
Let me just have a feel.

147
00:05:09,108 --> 00:05:10,108
Do it.

148
00:05:10,109 --> 00:05:11,708
Hey. What are you doing?

149
00:05:12,108 --> 00:05:13,148
Hey.

150
00:05:13,678 --> 00:05:15,548
Come on. Try harder.

151
00:05:16,048 --> 00:05:17,748
- Hey.
- It's not easy.

152
00:05:18,048 --> 00:05:19,048
What are you...

153
00:05:19,278 --> 00:05:20,788
It's not really working.

154
00:05:21,548 --> 00:05:23,717
- It can be done. For sure.
- For real?

155
00:05:23,718 --> 00:05:25,817
I don't think you can manage. Hang on. Let me see.

156
00:05:25,818 --> 00:05:26,827
Don't dunk me.

157
00:05:26,828 --> 00:05:28,957
- With my mouth...
- No, I'll...

158
00:05:28,958 --> 00:05:30,498
- Yes.
- What?

159
00:05:30,928 --> 00:05:32,228
Se Yoon, wait.

160
00:05:32,458 --> 00:05:33,697
- What?
- You'll do that?

161
00:05:33,698 --> 00:05:35,397
- Let me practice.
- Yes.

162
00:05:35,398 --> 00:05:36,697
Do it for real.

163
00:05:36,698 --> 00:05:38,667
- Okay.
- I got the angle, so one spin.

164
00:05:38,668 --> 00:05:40,307
- Do it properly.
- He's serious now.

165
00:05:40,308 --> 00:05:41,807
- This is a practice round.
- Two.

166
00:05:41,808 --> 00:05:43,907
You might rupture an eardrum, so cover your ears.

167
00:05:43,908 --> 00:05:45,338
He looks like a gorilla.

168
00:05:47,108 --> 00:05:49,047
- How was that?
- That'll do.

169
00:05:49,048 --> 00:05:50,077
You sliced the mandarin.

170
00:05:50,078 --> 00:05:52,418
- The mandarin's halved.
- He sliced it.

171
00:05:52,718 --> 00:05:53,718
Gosh.

172
00:05:53,719 --> 00:05:55,288
(A glancing blow halved it.)

173
00:05:55,348 --> 00:05:57,187
You might lose half your head.

174
00:05:57,188 --> 00:05:58,987
You cut the mandarin in half.

175
00:05:58,988 --> 00:06:00,688
It's not too bad a feat.

176
00:06:00,928 --> 00:06:03,328
We'll begin. Take your positions!

177
00:06:03,428 --> 00:06:05,298
Let's start the first try!

178
00:06:05,698 --> 00:06:07,567
Guys. We can do this.

179
00:06:07,568 --> 00:06:08,628
Do it, Seon Ho!

180
00:06:09,328 --> 00:06:11,237
(Feeling tense)

181
00:06:11,238 --> 00:06:12,438
Ready, go.

182
00:06:13,308 --> 00:06:14,367
(Participant 1 Seon Ho starts.)

183
00:06:14,368 --> 00:06:15,468
Good, Seon Ho!

184
00:06:16,938 --> 00:06:19,238
(Flapping up and down)

185
00:06:21,608 --> 00:06:22,748
(Now's the time!)

186
00:06:22,848 --> 00:06:23,848
(Zoom)

187
00:06:24,778 --> 00:06:25,778
(Zoom)

188
00:06:25,779 --> 00:06:28,248
(The stick won't give him time to eat.)

189
00:06:28,348 --> 00:06:30,187
(The next participants are getting nervous.)

190
00:06:30,188 --> 00:06:31,758
It must be so tiring.

191
00:06:32,718 --> 00:06:35,628
(Endless sit-ups until he eats the donut)

192
00:06:36,088 --> 00:06:37,158
- He can't...
- Wait.

193
00:06:38,798 --> 00:06:39,868
Come on.

194
00:06:40,598 --> 00:06:41,968
- He took a bite.
- Success!

195
00:06:43,668 --> 00:06:45,997
(He barely took a bite.)

196
00:06:45,998 --> 00:06:47,068
Hurry up.

197
00:06:47,708 --> 00:06:48,768
One, two, three.

198
00:06:49,538 --> 00:06:51,438
Do you think he can reach?

199
00:06:51,738 --> 00:06:53,247
You can start once Seon Ho starts jumping.

200
00:06:53,248 --> 00:06:55,024
(He must start jumping for the others to start.)

201
00:06:55,048 --> 00:06:56,477
(He hops in lightly.)

202
00:06:56,478 --> 00:06:58,018
- Okay.
- One, two, three.

203
00:06:58,748 --> 00:07:00,518
(Fashion muscles on full power)

204
00:07:00,688 --> 00:07:01,948
(Focused)

205
00:07:03,288 --> 00:07:04,658
You must move three balls.

206
00:07:05,388 --> 00:07:06,728
Again.

207
00:07:07,928 --> 00:07:09,528
- Is this good?
- It's fine.

208
00:07:09,958 --> 00:07:10,958
- Lower?
- Forward.

209
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:12,398
- Lift him higher.
- Forward?

210
00:07:13,098 --> 00:07:14,168
Done?

211
00:07:14,868 --> 00:07:15,868
You failed!

212
00:07:15,869 --> 00:07:16,938
- Why?
- What?

213
00:07:17,168 --> 00:07:18,438
Seon Ho tripped up.

214
00:07:18,698 --> 00:07:19,907
What's wrong with you?

215
00:07:19,908 --> 00:07:21,038
(What happened?)

216
00:07:21,438 --> 00:07:23,108
(Seon Ho was jumping leisurely.)

217
00:07:23,638 --> 00:07:24,778
Lift him higher.

218
00:07:25,538 --> 00:07:26,607
(Startled)

219
00:07:26,608 --> 00:07:28,277
(He failed for being too relaxed.)

220
00:07:28,278 --> 00:07:29,707
- What?
- What's wrong with you?

221
00:07:29,708 --> 00:07:30,748
(Boiling with anger)

222
00:07:30,948 --> 00:07:32,247
- What was that?
- What happened?

223
00:07:32,248 --> 00:07:33,347
Sorry.

224
00:07:33,348 --> 00:07:35,118
- Why did you trip up?
- What did you do?

225
00:07:35,348 --> 00:07:36,417
I was eating my donut.

226
00:07:36,418 --> 00:07:38,717
- Why did you keep eating?
- I should've minded the rope.

227
00:07:38,718 --> 00:07:40,188
I wanted to keep eating.

228
00:07:40,258 --> 00:07:42,257
- Let's give it another go.
- You have to tell me.

229
00:07:42,258 --> 00:07:43,757
- Yes.
- The balls keep moving.

230
00:07:43,758 --> 00:07:44,927
It's not too bad.

231
00:07:44,928 --> 00:07:46,227
- I think we can manage.
- Yes.

232
00:07:46,228 --> 00:07:47,228
The second time is easier.

233
00:07:47,229 --> 00:07:48,528
Let's do it in one go. I'm cold.

234
00:07:49,068 --> 00:07:50,798
This is your second try.

235
00:07:51,738 --> 00:07:53,468
We have a chance of making it.

236
00:07:54,838 --> 00:07:56,108
It's worth a try.

237
00:07:56,878 --> 00:07:57,937
(The spinning obstacle is running.)

238
00:07:57,938 --> 00:08:00,007
All right, start.

239
00:08:00,008 --> 00:08:01,008
Let's go, Seon Ho.

240
00:08:02,448 --> 00:08:04,617
Wait a minute. It hit my nose.

241
00:08:04,618 --> 00:08:06,077
- It's okay. You can do it.
- Take your time.

242
00:08:06,078 --> 00:08:07,188
We have enough time.

243
00:08:07,748 --> 00:08:08,948
It's okay.

244
00:08:09,348 --> 00:08:10,617
(The timing is difficult.)

245
00:08:10,618 --> 00:08:12,458
- Get hit and endure the pain.
- Seon Ho...

246
00:08:12,818 --> 00:08:14,358
Just get hit.

247
00:08:14,758 --> 00:08:16,188
Get hit instead of avoiding it.

248
00:08:16,928 --> 00:08:18,628
Hurry up. I want to do this.

249
00:08:19,158 --> 00:08:20,897
- Hurry up.
- This has to stop.

250
00:08:20,898 --> 00:08:21,927
Okay.

251
00:08:21,928 --> 00:08:23,238
(Full of fighting spirit)

252
00:08:23,668 --> 00:08:25,198
(He's almost there.)

253
00:08:26,438 --> 00:08:27,467
Okay.

254
00:08:27,468 --> 00:08:29,708
(Level 1 mission is cleared.)

255
00:08:29,908 --> 00:08:31,438
- Okay, he got it.
- Okay.

256
00:08:33,138 --> 00:08:34,707
You have to start the jump rope.

257
00:08:34,708 --> 00:08:36,408
- Start the jump rope.
- Concentrate.

258
00:08:37,518 --> 00:08:38,547
- All right, he's in.
- Go.

259
00:08:38,548 --> 00:08:39,548
Start.

260
00:08:39,549 --> 00:08:40,817
(Seon Ho starts the jump rope safely.)

261
00:08:40,818 --> 00:08:42,087
- Okay, go.
- One, two, three.

262
00:08:42,088 --> 00:08:43,858
(Level 2 starts.)

263
00:08:44,788 --> 00:08:46,788
(Tightening his lips)

264
00:08:47,958 --> 00:08:49,158
(Inhaling)

265
00:08:49,688 --> 00:08:50,958
Lift him up.

266
00:08:51,098 --> 00:08:52,457
Wrap your hands around his thighs.

267
00:08:52,458 --> 00:08:54,668
(He advances with all his might.)

268
00:08:56,298 --> 00:08:57,598
(They succeeded 1.)

269
00:08:58,638 --> 00:09:00,167
- Hurry up.
- You failed.

270
