814
00:28:08,302 --> 00:28:09,732
Nairobi is the capital of Kenya.

815
00:28:09,872 --> 00:28:11,132
- We just did two.
- My gosh.

816
00:28:11,902 --> 00:28:13,041
He lost weight.

817
00:28:13,042 --> 00:28:14,241
He lost 1kg.

818
00:28:14,242 --> 00:28:15,502
- No way.
- He lost 1kg?

819
00:28:15,672 --> 00:28:17,171
Hey, he really lost 1kg?

820
00:28:17,172 --> 00:28:18,172
