- Right.

840
00:28:50,112 --> 00:28:51,172
- Right.
- Yes.

841
00:28:51,472 --> 00:28:53,111
Let me check the menu first.

842
00:28:53,112 --> 00:28:54,141
Okay.

843
00:28:54,142 --> 00:28:56,111
There's another famous dish Chuncheon is known for...

844
00:28:56,112 --> 00:28:57,351
