851
00:29:05,952 --> 00:29:07,691
- We must get this.
- You'll eat dakgalbi...

852
00:29:07,692 --> 00:29:09,021
at a famous dakgalbi restaurant.

853
00:29:09,022 --> 00:29:10,908
- What? We're going to eat there?
- We'll go there?

854
00:29:10,932 --> 00:29:12,661
We will now begin with the Dinner Game,

855
00:29:12,662 --> 00:29:14,701
Dakgalbi Manipulation Squad.

856
00:29:14,702 --> 00:29:15,731
Dakgalbi Manipulation Squad?

857
00:29:15,732 --> 00:29:17,371
Your teamwork will be crucial...

858
00:29:17,372 --> 00:29:18,701
