863
00:29:25,712 --> 00:29:27,882
You'll play games to win additional ingredients.

864
00:29:28,182 --> 00:29:29,752
Like ramyeon noodles and rice cakes.

865
00:29:30,282 --> 00:29:31,881
(You can't have dakgalbi without additional toppings.)

866
00:29:31,882 --> 00:29:32,981
- Rice cakes, sweet potatoes, - Sweet potatoes.

867
00:29:32,982 --> 00:29:34,081
Udon noodles, mushrooms,

868
00:29:34,082 --> 00:29:35,481
- and cheese.
- My gosh.

869
00:29:35,482 --> 00:29:37,691
- I love cheese. We need cheese.
- I like dakgalbi with cheese.

870
00:29:37,692 --> 00:29:39,021
- Cheese is so good.
- I want udon noodles.

871
00:29:39,022 --> 00:29:40,521
