911
00:30:51,632 --> 00:30:53,261
- It's around 180cm.
- See? You guys can come close.

912
00:30:53,262 --> 00:30:54,262
- Okay.
- It could work.

913
00:30:54,263 --> 00:30:55,561
- Hey, we might be able to do it.
- It could work.

914
00:30:55,562 --> 00:30:57,072
- We got this.
- This is doable.

915
00:30:57,202 --> 00:30:58,631
I might be able to hit 2m on my own too.

916
00:30:58,632 --> 00:31:00,101
- You too.
- I think I can do it too.

917
00:31:00,102 --> 00:31:01,841
Let's do this. Let's try it.

918
00:31:01,842 --> 00:31:02,842
Okay. We'll try it.

919
00:31:02,842 --> 00:31:03,842
- Do your best.
- Let's try it.

920
00:31:03,842 --> 00:31:04,842
- Do your best.
- Okay.

921
00:31:04,843 --> 00:31:06,841
I'm getting the feeling we might be able to do this.

922
00:31:06,842 --> 00:31:09,411
- Let's do this.
- Our legs have to touch, right?

923
00:31:09,412 --> 00:31:10,412
- Let's do this.
- Yes.

924
00:31:10,413 --> 00:31:12,411
If your toes don't touch,

925
