935
00:31:28,133 --> 00:31:29,731
- Make sure they're touching.
- My gosh.

936
00:31:29,732 --> 00:31:31,502
- A little more. Move up more.
- Oh, my.

937
00:31:31,802 --> 00:31:34,372
Move up a little more. You can totally go for more.

938
00:31:34,802 --> 00:31:36,471
- No. You must bring it down.
