- I think we can do this.

942
00:31:41,982 --> 00:31:43,011
We got this.

943
00:31:43,012 --> 00:31:45,411
Jong Min, you can't move this leg.

944
00:31:45,412 --> 00:31:47,151
- Okay.
- You can't move this leg.

945
