989
00:33:09,402 --> 00:33:10,771
Let's try it once. If we fail, so be it.

990
00:33:10,772 --> 00:33:12,732
- Let's try it once. Let's do it.
- Let's go.

991
00:33:13,202 --> 00:33:14,701
- Let's do the leg split now.
- Yes.

992
00:33:14,702 --> 00:33:16,671
- Let's do it quickly.
- Let's do it one last time.

993
00:33:16,672 --> 00:33:18,371
Okay. Let's do our best.

994
00:33:18,372 --> 00:33:19,372
Okay.

995
00:33:19,373 --> 00:33:20,511
DinDin, try it one more time.

996
00:33:20,512 --> 00:33:21,811
- Just 1 more time.
- Just 1 more time.

997
00:33:21,812 --> 00:33:23,651
Just step 10cm past our record.

998
00:33:23,652 --> 00:33:24,811
- Okay.
- We'll try to beat our record.

999
00:33:24,812 --> 00:33:27,181
- I'm standing 10cm past our record.
- Okay.

1000
00:33:27,182 --> 00:33:29,352
- Let's do whatever it takes.
- Okay. We'll do it.

1001
00:33:29,652 --> 00:33:31,451
- Let's give it a try.
- It's a miracle...

1002
00:33:31,452 --> 00:33:33,862
