- It is. We tried really hard.

1003
00:33:34,292 --> 00:33:35,461
Let's finish this in one go.

1004
00:33:35,462 --> 00:33:37,591
(DinDin starts the mission without any complaints.)

1005
00:33:37,592 --> 00:33:39,232
Are you done?

1006
00:33:42,832 --> 00:33:44,301
(He tries to stretch out his legs as much as he can.)

1007
00:33:44,302 --> 00:33:45,302
(Their feet are touching.)

1008
00:33:45,303 --> 00:33:46,941
- Hurry up. Go ahead.
- This is as far as I can go.

1009
00:33:46,942 --> 00:33:48,501
- Hurry up and let's do this.
- Let's go.

1010
00:33:48,502 --> 00:33:49,641
- That's the best he can do?
- Help him.

1011
00:33:49,642 --> 00:33:50,948
- We can do this.
- Help Seon Ho.

1012
00:33:50,972 --> 00:33:52,642
One, two. That's good. That's it.

1013
00:33:53,112 --> 00:33:54,442
You must stretch a little more.

1014
00:33:55,282 --> 00:33:56,981
- Here I go.
- Hurry up. Jong Min.

1015
00:33:56,982 --> 00:33:58,942
(Seon Ho's and Jong Min's feet are touching too.)

1016
00:33:59,512 --> 00:34:02,281
(Jong Min tries to split his legs as much as possible.)

1017
00:34:02,282 --> 00:34:04,291
You need to keep going. A little more.

1018
00:34:04,292 --> 00:34:06,321
- You can do this. Keep going.
- Well done.

1019
00:34:06,322 --> 00:34:07,522
Put your toes down.

1020
00:34:08,292 --> 00:34:09,391
- They can do it.
- What?

1021
00:34:09,392 --> 00:34:10,932
- Hurry up.
- This is no joke.

1022
00:34:11,132 --> 00:34:12,932
- Hurry up.
- Measure it!

1023
00:34:13,732 --> 00:34:17,502
