1027
00:34:24,042 --> 00:34:25,542
- Run!
- Bring your foot closer.

1028
00:34:26,912 --> 00:34:28,642
- It's 15cm.
- It went over 15cm.

1029
00:34:29,012 --> 00:34:30,952
