Outdoors!

2539
01:29:07,956 --> 01:29:09,586
- Outdoors!
- Kim Jong Min!

2540
01:29:09,816 --> 01:29:12,826
(I can't believe this is the result of all my hard work.)

2541
01:29:13,386 --> 01:29:15,526
(Why is this happening to me?)

2542
01:29:15,956 --> 01:29:18,096
(Jong Min expects to sleep indoors.)

2543
01:29:18,626 --> 01:29:20,995
(The odds are 50 percent again.)

2544
01:29:20,996 --> 01:29:22,335
His life is full of luck.

2545
01:29:22,336 --> 01:29:24,706
(Life is a matter of luck.)

2546
01:29:28,276 --> 01:29:29,576
Gosh, his life.

2547
01:29:29,806 --> 01:29:31,976
His life is full of luck.

2548
01:29:32,576 --> 01:29:34,645
You'd better not pick indoors.

2549
01:29:34,646 --> 01:29:37,345
- I'm just lucky. I can't help it.
- Don't pick indoors.

2550
01:29:37,346 --> 01:29:39,515
I didn't do anything. I can't help it.

2551
01:29:39,516 --> 01:29:40,885
(I don't want to sleep outdoors without him.)

2552
01:29:40,886 --> 01:29:42,315
Don't pick indoors.

2553
01:29:42,316 --> 01:29:43,985
- You didn't open it yet, right?
- I didn't.

2554
01:29:43,986 --> 01:29:46,026
(Now there are only two left.)

2555
01:29:46,826 --> 01:29:48,572
- Please. It has to be Joon.
- Do you want to switch?

2556
01:29:48,596 --> 01:29:49,955
- What?
- What?

2557
01:29:49,956 --> 01:29:51,526
This is big. What do you say?

2558
01:29:52,166 --> 01:29:53,226
I'll switch.

2559
01:29:54,036 --> 01:29:55,936
(Switched)

2560
01:29:56,366 --> 01:29:59,706
(Intriguing)

2561
01:30:00,236 --> 01:30:03,135
- Are you serious?
- The fate is already decided.

2562
01:30:03,136 --> 01:30:05,382
If he sleeps indoors like this, it will be even more upsetting.

2563
01:30:05,406 --> 01:30:07,245
- All right.
- I didn't do anything.

2564
01:30:07,246 --> 01:30:08,745
I just got what was left...

2565
01:30:08,746 --> 01:30:10,246
and switched it as he said.

2566
01:30:10,986 --> 01:30:13,546
- Okay. I agree.
- I didn't do anything.

2567
01:30:13,656 --> 01:30:15,185
I'm really nervous.

2568
01:30:15,186 --> 01:30:17,085
This is like the Drawing Groups. This is crazy.

2569
01:30:17,086 --> 01:30:19,055
- You guys switched it.
- We switched it.

2570
01:30:19,056 --> 01:30:21,596
Please. It has to be Lee Joon.

2571
01:30:22,056 --> 01:30:23,826
Otherwise, I'll be too furious to sleep!

2572
01:30:24,226 --> 01:30:25,465
It has to be Lee Joon.

2573
01:30:25,466 --> 01:30:27,936
- I didn't do anything.
- Don't let it be Jong Min.

2574
01:30:28,466 --> 01:30:30,606
One, two, three.

2575
01:30:36,036 --> 01:30:37,776
(Indoors, outdoors)

2576
01:30:37,806 --> 01:30:39,245
(Indoors)

2577
01:30:39,246 --> 01:30:40,716
(What?)

2578
01:30:41,146 --> 01:30:43,476
(Kim Jong Min gets to sleep indoors.)

2579
01:30:43,886 --> 01:30:46,716
(A shocking result)

2580
01:30:47,116 --> 01:30:49,016
(Devastated)

2581
01:30:49,056 --> 01:30:50,685
This is insane.

2582
01:30:50,686 --> 01:30:52,026
I didn't know.

2583
01:30:52,426 --> 01:30:54,596
- I didn't do anything.
- How is this possible?

2584
01:30:54,896 --> 01:30:57,126
This is insane.

2585
01:30:57,626 --> 01:30:58,665
(Those who work hard can't beat those who are lucky.)

2586
01:30:58,666 --> 01:31:00,025
It was a great match.

2587
01:31:00,026 --> 01:31:01,436
- My goodness.
- All right.

2588
01:31:01,836 --> 01:31:03,436
Joon shouldn't have switched it.

2589
01:31:03,936 --> 01:31:06,036
He didn't do anything.

2590
01:31:06,336 --> 01:31:08,075
All you did was sleep with your head down on the pillow.

2591
01:31:08,076 --> 01:31:10,405
Yes, I slept. I didn't say anything.

2592
01:31:10,406 --> 01:31:12,006
(Shameless)

2593
01:31:12,376 --> 01:31:14,676
So, here's the result of the draw.

2594
01:31:15,346 --> 01:31:17,446
DinDin, Se Yoon, and Joon...

2595
01:31:17,986 --> 01:31:19,316
will sleep outdoors.

2596
01:31:19,616 --> 01:31:21,115
It's Jong Min and me again.

2597
01:31:21,116 --> 01:31:22,785
(Seon Ho and Jong Min sleep indoors.)

2598
01:31:22,786 --> 01:31:24,625
- This is unbelievable.
- He's so lucky.

2599
01:31:24,626 --> 01:31:26,856
Seriously, you're unbelievable.

2600
01:31:26,886 --> 01:31:29,655
- Really...
- You're truly amazing.

2601
01:31:29,656 --> 01:31:30,772
(What on earth is with him?)

2602
01:31:30,796 --> 01:31:32,996
- I'll see you tomorrow morning.
- All right.

2603
01:31:33,166 --> 01:31:35,396
- Goodnight.
- Thank you.

2604
01:31:35,866 --> 01:31:36,996
Goodnight.

2605
01:31:37,666 --> 01:31:40,166
(Team Indoors enters the barracks.)

2606
01:31:41,836 --> 01:31:42,876
