2643
01:32:50,576 --> 01:32:51,705
(Let's manipulate the results without Jong Min.)

2644
01:32:51,706 --> 01:32:53,546
If it doesn't work, let's just give up.

2645
01:32:53,846 --> 01:32:55,016
I don't think it will work.

2646
01:32:56,716 --> 01:32:57,915
I'm hungry.

2647
01:32:57,916 --> 01:32:58,962
(It was an unusually eventful day.)

2648
01:32:58,986 --> 01:33:01,056
- Goodnight.
- You went through a lot today.

2649
01:33:01,216 --> 01:33:03,756
- Goodnight.
- Goodnight.

2650
01:33:03,856 --> 01:33:05,756
(Next episode)

2651
