2661
01:33:29,076 --> 01:33:30,986
(Why would you do that?)

2662
01:33:32,246 --> 01:33:35,456
(A harsh yet warm winter workshop of 2 Days 1 Night)

2663
01:33:36,356 --> 01:33:38,156
(He's the type who's proud of his face.)

2664
01:33:39,786 --> 01:33:41,055
